==Herbert and the Dark Mage==
===Talking to the Mage of Zamorak===
* '''Mage of Zamorak:''' Ah, you again. What do you want?
* {{topt|I need your help with an amulet.}}
** '''Player:''' I need your help with an amulet.
** '''Mage of Zamorak:''' An amulet? What amulet?
** {{tcond|If the player doesn't have the amulet:}}
*** '''Player:''' Oh, I don't actually have it with me. I'll be back.
*** '''Mage of Zamorak:''' Right...
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{tbox|pic=Eye amulet detail.png|You show the amulet to the Mage of Zamorak.}}
** '''Mage of Zamorak:''' That eye on it... That is the symbol of the Order of Wizards. What's all this about?
** '''Player:''' The amulet is giving off abyssal energy. I was hoping you could help me work out where it came from.
** '''Mage of Zamorak:''' Why should I?
** '''Player:''' Well I did help you gain access to the Rune Essence Mine.
** '''Mage of Zamorak:''' And we gave you knowledge on the Abyss in return. We owe you no further favours.
** '''Player:''' Are you not even slightly curious about how an amulet with the symbol of the Order of Wizards on it is giving off abyssal energy? After all, they don't have access to the Abyss.
** '''Mage of Zamorak:''' I hope you're not about to tell me that you shared our secrets with the Saradominists?
** '''Player:''' Of course not.
** '''Mage of Zamorak:''' Then where did you get the amulet?
** '''Player:''' I... bought it from an archaeologist.
** '''Mage of Zamorak:''' There's something off about all of this. Show it to me again.
** {{tbox|pic=Eye amulet detail.png|You show the amulet to the Mage of Zamorak again. As you do, he casts a spell upon it.}}
** '''Player:''' What was that?
** '''Mage of Zamorak:''' Just a spell to tell me more about it. It seems this amulet is very unusual.
** '''Player:''' So you'll help?
** '''Mage of Zamorak:''' Very well, but first you must do something for me. Bring me a bucket of water and a strong cup of tea.
** '''Player:''' A strong cup of tea?
** '''Mage of Zamorak:''' That's right. The tea seller just north east of here can give you one. He owes me, in fact, so just tell him Herbert sent you.
** '''Player:''' Wait... Your name is Herbert?
** '''Mage of Zamorak:''' Is that a problem?
** '''Player:''' I guess not. I just never had you down as a Herbert.
** {{topt|quest=No|Can you tell me more about the Abyss?}}
** {{topt|quest=No|Can you tell me more about your group?}}
** {{topt|I'll be back soon.}}
*** '''Player:''' I'll be back soon.
*** {{tact|end}}
