===Talking to the Dark Mage===
* '''Player:''' Hello there.
* '''Dark Mage:''' Quiet! You must not break my concentration!
* {{topt|quest=No|Why not?}}
* {{topt|quest=No|What are you doing here?}}
* {{topt|I need your help with an amulet.}}
** '''Player:''' I need your help with an amulet.
** '''Dark Mage:''' Amulet?
** {{tcond|If the player does not have the amulet:}}
*** '''Player:''' Yes, but I don't seem to have it with me. I'll be back soon.
