** '''Dark Mage:''' Oh, hang on. Someone is trying to contact me...
** {{tbox|The Dark Mage suddenly starts talking to someone else.}}
** '''Dark Mage:''' What do you want? Can't you see I'm busy?
** '''Dark Mage:''' Fine. A simple transfiguration spell should resolve things for you.
** '''Dark Mage:''' Now can you leave me alone? I can't keep affording these distractions!
** {{tbox|The Dark Mage turns back to you.}}
** '''Dark Mage:''' What did you want? Something about an amulet?
** '''Player:''' Yes, but first...
** {{tbox|pic=Bucket of water detail.png|You throw the bucket of water over the Dark Mage.}}
** '''Dark Mage:''' What in the actual...
** '''Player:''' Sorry, but Herbert said you needed a wash.
** '''Dark Mage:''' Are you serious? What if I'd lost concentration and let this rift collapse? Do you like having a brain that isn't made of mush? Because mush is all that would have been left!
** '''Player:''' I like my brain how it is, thanks. Now, could you help me?
** '''Dark Mage:''' Why should I? I'm soaked thanks to you!
** '''Player:''' Herbert said you would.
** '''Dark Mage:''' Of course he did! Alright then, what do you want?
** '''Player:''' This amulet is giving off abyssal energy. I need you to cast a spell to tell me where it came from.
** '''Dark Mage:''' Let's have a look then.
** {{tbox|pic=Eye amulet detail.png|You show the amulet to the Dark Mage.}}
** '''Dark Mage:''' Right, just give me a moment.
** {{tbox|pic=Eye amulet detail.png|The Dark Mage casts a spell on the amulet.}}
** '''Dark Mage:''' Okay, this spell will allow me to triangulate the origin of the amulet. To make things easier, I'm using this rift to compare energy from that origin with energy from the runic altars.
** '''Dark Mage:''' Of course, thanks to the ways time and space work in this place, the information won't necessarily come in the right order.
** '''Player:''' Meaning?
** '''Dark Mage:''' Meaning I'll need you to help, you fool! You see that energy that's just emerged from the rift? Work out which order it goes in!
** '''Player:''' Right...
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|quest=No|I need your help with something.}}
* {{topt|quest=No|Sorry, I'll go.}}

