===Closing the rift===
* {{qact|A cutscene plays. The Great Guardian prepares to close the rift.}}
* '''The Great Guardian:''' Humans, I now have the power to close the rift. Brace yourselves!
* {{qact|The Great Guardian shoots a beam towards the rift, and it fades away.}}
* '''The Great Guardian:''' We are safe, for now.
* '''Apprentice Tamara:''' What was all that? What happened?
* '''The Great Guardian:''' That was a rift into an area of the Abyss known as the Scar.
* '''Apprentice Cordelia:''' The Scar? But I thought this was meant to be a teleportation matrix.
* '''The Great Guardian:''' You are mistaken. While it is true that teleportation magic is strong here, that is only a side effect of this temple's history.
* '''Apprentice Felix:''' What history?
* '''The Great Guardian:''' This temple was built to house a powerful artefact. Many sought to claim this artefact for themselves, including servants of the Fallen Empire.
* '''The Great Guardian:''' In their attempt to claim the artefact, they used magic they did not understand. The rift to the Scar was created as a result.
* '''Player:''' This artefact... you mean the Eye?
* '''The Great Guardian:''' You are correct. The Eye was removed after the battle, but not before the Justiciar of the Lion used it to seal the rift once more.
* '''The Great Guardian:''' She then created us, the Guardians of the Rift, to protect this place in the event the rift was ever reopened.
* '''Apprentice Felix:''' And we reopened it.
* '''Apprentice Cordelia:''' But it's been sealed again now! The danger is gone.
* '''The Great Guardian:''' Incorrect. Without the power of the Eye, we have no way to seal the rift permanently. It will soon reopen once more. You should leave before that happens.
* '''Apprentice Tamara:''' No. This was our mistake. I'm staying to help fix it.
* '''Apprentice Felix:''' Me too!
* '''Apprentice Cordelia:''' Well if you two are staying, I guess I will as well.
* '''The Great Guardian:''' Your support will be invaluable.
* '''Apprentice Tamara:''' [player name], could you go back to the Wizards' Tower and let Sedridor know what happened here?
* '''Player:''' Alright, if you're absolutely sure about this.
* '''Apprentice Felix:''' What about Persten? We have to help her.
* '''The Great Guardian:''' No part of the Abyss is more dangerous than the Scar. Your friend will have already been consumed.
* '''The Great Guardian:''' Now, the power of the Abyss grows. The rift will soon reopen once more. Those of you staying should prepare yourselves.
* '''Player:''' Then I guess I'd better go and see Sedridor. Good luck.
