===Sedridor cutscene===
* '''Player:''' Sedridor! It all went wrong!
* '''Archmage Sedridor:''' What do you mean? Was there no teleportation matrix?
* '''Player:''' Kind of, but not really. The portal took us to the Temple of the Eye, an ancient Saradominist temple built to house a powerful artefact.
* '''Player:''' Long ago, a rift to the Abyss was created in the temple, but it was sealed. At least it was, until Persten accidently opened it again...
* '''Player:''' She was sucked into the Abyss, and all these abyssal creatures came out!
* '''Archmage Sedridor:''' Abyssal creatures? We have to get in there and stop this!
* '''Player:''' It's okay again, for now. Some rune guardians called the Guardians of the Rift were built to protect the temple from the Abyss. They helped us close the rift again, but they say it will soon reopen.
* '''Archmage Sedridor:''' This is a disaster! I knew that teleportation matrix was too good to be true. I should have stopped this, but I was blinded by my own desires for that matrix!
* '''Archmage Sedridor:''' What of Traiborn's apprentices?
* '''Player:''' They're safe. They chose to stay and help the Guardians of the Rift keep the rift closed.
* '''Archmage Sedridor:''' Then I will ensure they have all the help they need. I will also begin researching this rift at once. Maybe we can still find a way to close it permanently.
* '''Archmage Sedridor:''' In the meantime, I suggest you do what you can to help them as well. After all, this is partially your doing.
* '''Player:''' I know. I'll help wherever I'm needed.
* '''Archmage Sedridor:''' Thank you, [player name]. I appreciate that you did not mean for things to go this way. You should have this. It belonged to Persten. I don't want to think about where she got it.
* {{tbox|pic=Medium pouch detail.png|Sedridor shows you a pouch.}}
* '''Player:''' Do you think she's still alive?
* '''Archmage Sedridor:''' Sadly, that seems unlikely. Still, if anyone can survive the Abyss, it's her.
* '''Archmage Sedridor:''' Now, we'd better get to work.
* {{Qact|Congratulations! Quest complete!}}

